ia Route 329|Route 329]]  \n*[[Nova Scotia Route 330|Route 330]]  \n*[[Nova Scotia Route 331|Route 331]]\n*[[Nova Scotia Route 332|Route 332]]\n*[[Nova Scotia Route 333|Route 333]]\n\n===Named Roads===\n*Brighton Road\n*East Green Harbour Road\n*Little Harbour Road\n*Port Clyde Road\n*Sandy Point Road\n*Shore Road\n*West Sable Road\n\n==List of Communities (east to west)==\n{{div col|colwidth=20em}}\n*[[Halifax Urban Area|Halifax]]\n*[[Halifax Peninsula]]\n*[[Armdale, Nova Scotia|Armdale]]\n* [[Mainland Halifax]]\n*[[Beechville, Nova Scotia|Beechville]]\n*[[Goodwood, Nova Scotia|Goodwood]]\n*[[Hatchet Lake, Nova Scotia|Hatchet Lake]]\n*[[Whites Lake, Nova Scotia|Whites lake]]\n*[[Shad Bay, Nova Scotia|Shad Bay]]\n*[[Bayside, Nova Scotia|Bayside]]\n*[[Peggys Cove, Nova Scotia|Peggys Cove]]\n*[[Indian Harbour, Nova Scotia|Indian Harbour]]\n*[[Hackett's Cove, Nova Scotia|Hackett's Cove]]\n*[[Glen Margaret, Nova Scotia|Glen Margaret]]\n*[[Seabright, Nova Scotia|Seabright]]\n*[[French Village, Nova Scotia|French Village]]\n*[[Glen Haven, Nova Scotia|Glen Haven]]\n*[[Tantallon, Nova Scotia|Tantallon]]\n*[[Upper Tantallon, Nova Scotia|Upper Tantallon]]\n*[[Hubbards, Nova Scotia|Hubbards]]\n*[[Aldersville, Nova Scotia|Aldersville]]\n*[[Aspotogan, Nova Scotia|Aspotogan]]\n*[[Bayswater, Nova Scotia|Bayswater]]\n*[[Beech Hill, Nova Scotia|Beech Hill]]\n*[[Blandford, Nova Scotia|Blandford]]\n*[[Chester, Nova Scotia (community)|Chester]]\n*[[Chester Basin, Nova Scotia|Chester Basin]]\n*[[Chester Grant, Nova Scotia|Chester Grant]]\n*[[Deep Cove, Nova Scotia|Deep Cove]]\n*[[East River, Nova Scotia|East River]]\n*[[Forties Settlement, Nova Scotia|Forties Settlement]]\n*[[Fox Point, Nova Scotia|Fox Point]]\n*[[Mill Cove, Nova Scotia|Mill Cove]]\n*[[Mill Road, Nova Scotia|Mill Road]]\n*[[New Ross, Nova Scotia|New Ross]]\n*[[New Russell, Nova Scotia|New Russell]]\n*[[Northwest Cove, Nova Scotia|Northeast Cove]]\n*[[Petite Riviere, Nova Scotia|Petite Riviere]]\n*[[Crescent Beach, Nova 